    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A novel game where a rabbit girl and various characters spend time together.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[★Synopsis★]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character, Kosuke Tamaki, has advanced to his second year of high school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He finds an injured rabbit while walking in the forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When I took him home and let him rest, what was the person standing in front of me the next morning?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please enjoy the relaxing daily life of the characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play time will be approximately 1 hour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【★Rest House★】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >scenario:Mov Ken</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >illustration:Kinakousa</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[★Voice actor★]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yukino Suzuka</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Furugori</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[★Composer of the music used★]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rabbit shop music room</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharou</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ucchii0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[★Author of background material used★]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minchirie</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The characters, organizations, names, etc. that appear are fictitious and have nothing to do with reality.</p>",
